description: AMUNDI INDEX MSCI EUROPE - UCITS ETF DR seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI Europe Index, total return (dividends reinvested), in EUR, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to the large and mid-cap markets of the developed European countries. For further information, please also refer to the KID and the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi Index MSCI Europe UCITS ETF DR (C)
